9. Open Questions & Risks 
9.1 Open Questions 
• Reel download mechanism: Several third-party services offer unofficial Instagram reel  download APIs. A vendor needs to be evaluated for reliability, ToS exposure, and rate  limits before development begins. 
• Whisper cost at scale: At high save volumes, transcription costs could become significant.  Cost modelling should be done before launch. 
• Category confidence threshold: The 0.75 threshold is an initial assumption. This should  be calibrated on real data during beta. 
9.2 Risks 
• Instagram API restrictions: Instagram has historically been aggressive about blocking  unofficial data access. The share sheet approach (URL-only) is the safest available  option, but it still depends on the reel being publicly accessible. Any change to  Instagram's URL scheme or access controls could break ingestion.
