• Content becoming unavailable: A reel saved today may be deleted or account-privated  tomorrow. The transcript is retained, but the 'Watch Reel' link degrades. This is a known  and accepted limitation for MVP. 
• LLM hallucination in query responses: The LLM must be prompted to answer only from  provided context and to clearly label web-sourced content. Hallucinated product  recommendations are a reputational risk. RAG architecture mitigates but does not  eliminate this. 
